sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant CDN
    participant Gateway as API Gateway
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant API as REST API
    participant Cache as Redis Cache
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>Browser: Click Login
    Browser->>Gateway: POST /api/auth/login
    Gateway->>Auth: Validate credentials
    Auth->>DB: SELECT user WHERE email = ?
    DB-->>Auth: User record
    alt Invalid credentials
        Auth-->>Gateway: 401 Unauthorized
        Gateway-->>Browser: Error response
        Browser-->>User: Show error message
    else Valid credentials
        Auth->>Auth: Generate JWT + Refresh Token
        Auth->>Cache: Store refresh token (TTL: 7d)
        Auth-->>Gateway: 200 OK {token, refreshToken}
        Gateway-->>Browser: Set-Cookie + JSON
        Browser-->>User: Redirect to Dashboard
    end

    Note over User,DB: User is now authenticated

    User->>Browser: View Profile
    Browser->>CDN: GET /static/profile.js
    CDN-->>Browser: JavaScript bundle
    Browser->>Gateway: GET /api/user/profile
    Gateway->>Gateway: Verify JWT
    Gateway->>Cache: Check cached profile
    alt Cache Hit
        Cache-->>Gateway: Cached profile data
    else Cache Miss
        Gateway->>API: Forward request
        API->>DB: SELECT * FROM profiles
        DB-->>API: Profile data
        API->>Cache: SET profile (TTL: 5min)
        API-->>Gateway: Profile JSON
    end
    Gateway-->>Browser: Profile response
    Browser-->>User: Render profile page

    loop Every 30 minutes
        Browser->>Gateway: POST /api/auth/refresh
        Gateway->>Auth: Validate refresh token
        Auth->>Cache: Check token exists
        Cache-->>Auth: Token valid
        Auth-->>Gateway: New JWT
        Gateway-->>Browser: Updated token
    end
